# Frontend env vars. Copy to `.env.local` and adjust.
# Vite only exposes vars prefixed with VITE_ to the browser.

# Base URL of the backend API. In dev, leave empty to use the Vite proxy (vite.config.ts proxies /api -> http://localhost:3201).
# In production, set this to the public URL of your backend, e.g. https://api.onekeytoeverywhere.com
# VITE_API_URL=
